Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:04.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这 这个我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这张超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,简直就是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱大人太不妙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这全都是心寿拍的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我超喜欢心寿拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:28.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我当初只是请她拍照而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结果她就帮我创了我的COS名和账号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:34.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为姐姐都不想给别人看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:44.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我想着 "想让人看看姐姐可爱的照片"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就问姐姐能不能帮她办账号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:50.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然后就有好多人点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:50.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第一次投稿)\N然后就有好多人点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(目前拍的里面最喜欢的4张)\N然后就有好多人点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(变成人鱼了)\N然后就有好多人点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很多人都称赞了姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:02.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是不知道要怎么回复陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就全都忽视了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才没和任何人有来往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是为了自我满足才COS的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他人的评价怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追随者也增加了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想说姐姐果然很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就觉得很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心寿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:25.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:29.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你超喜欢朱朱大人的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:32.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朱朱大人很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少 少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,闪耀着璀璨色彩的重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:54.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不会忘记的 没错 就是这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在水平线的遥远彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:09.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,流露的叹息随着波浪消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:14.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你找出了我隐藏的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:20.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,并牵起我的手向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:26.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,满面笑容的你映入了眼帘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:31.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,波浪溅起时的两个身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:36.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,响起的脚步声迈向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:43.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不断追逐着阳光下赤脚的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:48.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,敞开心胸泼起了水花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:53.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,烂漫摇曳的水面染上璀璨色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:59.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,初次相遇了这种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:04.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真挚地注视着梦想的美丽双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:09.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想在你身旁相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Be myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第8话 我推荐逆光拍)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相机是向爸爸借的单反相机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你爸爸是摄影师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 拍照只是他的兴趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:30.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为这是不用换镜头的相机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,镜头是需要换的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以依照喜好更换哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(鱼眼 标准 望远)\N只要交换镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(鱼眼 标准 望远)\N即便是相同的角度拍也会有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(鱼眼 标准 望远)\N很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:42.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和用手机拍摄还是差很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为画质还是比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能做到的表现比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如像是以花为背景拍摄时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就可以用散景强调COSER本身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,让前景的部分失焦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拍出有温柔氛围的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要调整快门速度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也可以清楚的拍下飘落的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感觉很有趣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:14.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,顺利拍出自己想要的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或是拍下意外的好表情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会想要拍得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拍出更可爱的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且拍的是朱朱大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是让人有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,话说心寿不COS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:39.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看着别人COS不会也想COS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起来超可爱 很开心不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想说"我也想要"之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心寿也想COS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不会想COS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢拍姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心寿 可以让我摸一下相机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相机真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想拍出漂亮的散景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要存钱 绝对要买!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,单反相机大概要多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:20.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(镜头另售)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,镜头另售!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:32.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太大声了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果要买脚架和闪光灯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还要更多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学都目瞪口呆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家在之前的活动里拿着的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然是这么昂贵的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是不妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,总之在存到钱之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还是先用手机拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同学毫不犹豫地决定要买啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相机的有很多种 价差很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,选个预算内的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-谢谢惠顾 -我们要去场勘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你们也要一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为是第一次租摄影棚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以觉得先去看看比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:14.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我绝对要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请务必让我们同行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那周末在新三乡站会合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们要去的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,废弃医院摄影棚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来还有这种摄影棚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次到废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常期待今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上都睡不太着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-比想象得更阴暗呢 -和输给公主雏菊的右直拳时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逃进的废弃医院一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然是很灰暗的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我很喜欢紫苑输掉后自问自答的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,话说你真的全都看完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学 我们去上面看看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,走吧 心寿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-好的 -真是有气氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,干同学该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不擅长应付这种地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来不擅长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是不是反而太暗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为有闪光灯所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,简直无敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:52.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,闪光灯和反光板也能用在户外的摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有买的话比较方便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算外面是晴天也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:55.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天气好的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会因为太亮而睁不开眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以要逆光拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肌肤的质感看起来也会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:13.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但这样的话脸就会变暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以才要用反光板打光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,假发也会透光变得闪闪发亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,光泽也会变得更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那超棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也告诉五条同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很推荐逆光拍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想在拍起来好看的地方拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,话说心寿你们去外拍的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都去哪里拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们家的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,干同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没 没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是有点累而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看起来不像没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你要回去入口等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好不容易能出黑百合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要好好确认里面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不然就没办法拍出好照片不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我会确认好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请在入口等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 我要自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是你在勉强自己对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什么理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有将来的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:41.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想成为娃娃的头师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,制作娃娃脸部的工匠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是个很棒的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,绝对要实现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我曾梦想成为魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既厉害又闪闪发光的很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,穿着蓬蓬的可爱衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小时候就很憧憬着魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看得非常着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,认真地想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"我长大之后要成为魔法少女"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是上了小学就知道了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那全都是创造出来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便像魔法少女一样努力 祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的梦想也是永远不会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是升上国中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我发现有在卖魔法少女的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为没有相关知识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,连假发要修整都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也没有化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服装的尺寸也不合身松垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然第一次的COS不堪入目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:07.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便如此我还是由衷地感到开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算全都是创作出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我还是想实现我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,干同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明是那么重要的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么要委托我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还有很多比我更厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,虽然事到如今 应该去委托其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么要委托我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:38.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我看到喜多川海梦她的照片时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嫉妒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也知道嫉妒什么的很不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但真的羨慕到难以自制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想着"我也想穿这个人做的服装"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"非这个人做的衣服不行"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的确有很多会做服装的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也无法好好说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讲不出个所以然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我一定是在那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对你做的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我对自己会嫉妒也很惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:27.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但人不会对不在乎的东西嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这个女儿节娃娃是爷爷们做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是世界上最漂亮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界上最漂亮的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是爷爷为了让客人在众多的娃娃店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,眼睛为之一亮而停下目光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:58.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜欢到觉得"这个娃娃是最棒的"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而拼了命做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你能说是最美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:05.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爷爷很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,停下目光是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是让人一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等我长大之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想变得会做娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想变得像爷爷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:36.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新菜只要练习也能变得像爷爷一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等…怎么了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为什么你在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:50.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:51.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我现在终于知道那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爷爷有多开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原来是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,为了有一天能被那么称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-一定会… -干纱寿叶 17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就读女子完全中学的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被年龄相仿的异性握住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,干同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-五条同学 雷超大声的 你们没事吧 -怎么了吗 干同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-五条同学 雷超大声的 你们没事吧 -你没事吧 干同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了 考完了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我们去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,现在去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为海水浴场还没开放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全没有人超棒的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,简直就像是包场一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天是来拍照的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,场勘的时候说了想要逆光拍摄对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在拍起来好看的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 完全没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,期末考不是考完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,现在不是7月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正值夏天对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:33.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,穿着制服来海边玩不是很青春吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:41.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没错!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喜多川同学就是这种人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何等行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学 也给我些薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,薯条 薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的汉堡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,还在跟着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去远一点的地方吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 都难得来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:18.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不就会想边看海边喝珍奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且连野餐垫都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又被抢走的时候再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,薯条就放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,趁现在离远一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,汉堡还剩下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不小心就乱丢垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老鹰先生再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这是五条同学的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超级好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,汉堡和魩仔鱼真搭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,珍奶真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学要喝一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用了 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,海风吹起来好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下去海里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帮我拿这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,踩踩水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为一时兴起所以也没带泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是随兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你看 超大的海带芽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有在看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超级棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,海浪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,脚渐渐沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也太吃惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是第一次来海边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧? 真假?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,说起来埼玉也没有海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我从小时候就只顾着看娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:29.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,学爷爷练习画脸觉得非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一直沉浸在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,没有把其他事物放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以有很多没去过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:47.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之前爷爷叫我要多看看其他东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,和电视还有照片上看到的完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大海真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那和我一起去各种各样的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,马 马上就是暑假对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…会一直约你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,两 两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,请你多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:39.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好像有些口渴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我去喝点茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:42.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:53.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,顺 顺势就说了要两个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙 不妙 超不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是被发现脸红的话好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好害羞 好害羞 好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,这样暑假能一直见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我会受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全身 全身都是海带芽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,粘答答 粘答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:52.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五条同学你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我 我想走进更深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,结果就踩到海带芽跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要怎么回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,会干的 会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:04.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,应该
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,U FU FU FU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不经意地发现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定是陷入了恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因为命运的作弄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:34.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,对那一句话怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:40.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不能再更期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:45.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,现在两人追寻着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:50.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一心一意纯洁的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:53.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,渐渐动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:57.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好 不小心就对你一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:00.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太喜欢你了 该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,坦率面对自己内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以啊 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:15.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在身旁看着含苞待放的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,NANANA NANANA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,U FU FU FU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(第9话)\N(看了照片之后发生了些事)